trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>, an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> or an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: It specifies the schema for XML messages that are not SOAP compliant.
trans-unit.target: 它會指定不是 SOAP 相容的 XML 訊息的結構描述。

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"></xref> class.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> to which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"></xref> applies.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定名稱<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref>的<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"></xref>套用。
